{"tid":1859362,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢肺炎：中國留學生「扮港人」成功入境 澳洲","createTime":"2020-02-03T08:09:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T08:23:32.000Z","uid":226548,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4da9170445dd4ebe1373c9f7288e4d34e26aea57","tid":1859362,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T08:09:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/F9TWSW_W.oeLOiZz.dsYbQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQ1Ni44NDIxMDUyNjMxNTc5/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/7lNN5Sz1oLOEnwKU8NKFEg--~B/aD00MzQ7dz02MDg7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-02/95df43b0-464b-11ea-ba69-85e89e8f4ddc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FF9TWSW_W.oeLOiZz.dsYbQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQ1Ni44NDIxMDUyNjMxNTc5%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F7lNN5Sz1oLOEnwKU8NKFEg--~B%2FaD00MzQ7dz02MDg7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-02%2F95df43b0-464b-11ea-ba69-85e89e8f4ddc&h=56ed8b3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n澳洲政府因應武漢肺炎疫情，上周六（1日）宣布禁止非公民、永久居民及其直系親屬入境，大批中國留學生受影響。澳媒報道，一名中國留學生經香港轉機返回澳洲昆士蘭，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">過關前將入境登記卡的出境地改為香港</span></strong>，結果成功獲澳洲海關放行。<br />\n<br />\n該名化名小K的留學生透露，他在禁令生效當晚11時許抵達布里斯班，落機後才得知消息。小K的同學甚至傳送訊息，嘲笑他將要被遣返；惟他臨急生智，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">將入境登記卡上的「CHINA」劃掉並改為「HONG KONG」</span></strong>，結果關員只看了他一眼，便允許他從另一側通道入境，連行李都沒有檢查。<br />\n<br />\n其他受訪的留學生則運氣較差，同樣在昆士蘭讀書的小輝，當日從上海啟程並經香港轉機到布里斯班，在落地前1小時澳洲政府才宣布限制令。惟小輝經轉機抵達，而行李卻直達澳洲，無法入境的情況下無法取回行李。小輝與幾名同胞最後被海關帶進「小黑屋」，在對方要求下即場購票返程，再由航空公司轉運行李。"},{"pid":"3900039f1acaec6c9df3229f329f2f0bc4be9369","tid":1859362,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T08:10:04.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/home/武漢肺炎中國留學生扮港人入境-獲澳洲海關放行-060851450.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fhome%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%95%99%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%89%AE%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83-%E7%8D%B2%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E6%B5%B7%E9%97%9C%E6%94%BE%E8%A1%8C-060851450.html&d=sSzAGq%2B8hAhXqg0aovu9KfrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=ec831f3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/home/武漢肺炎中國留學生扮港人入境-獲澳洲海關放行-060851450.html</a>"},{"pid":"7b9f1bb1232d66cab06a591b988483a4371d156d","tid":1859362,"uid":255976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T08:23:32.000Z","msg":"香港人快=大陸人，全球禁入境。"}]}